<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document Verification Update - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .status-verified {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .status-rejected {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        .document-details {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .verification-info {
            background-color: #e8f4f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .rejection-reason {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üìÑ Document Verification Update</h1>
        <p>Status update for your submitted document</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="status-<%= status %>" style="padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h2>
                <% if (status === 'verified') { %>
                    ‚úÖ Document Verified
                <% } else if (status === 'rejected') { %>
                    ‚ùå Document Rejected
                <% } %>
            </h2>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Hello <%= contactName %>,</h2>
        
        <p>We have completed the review of your document submission. Here are the details:</p>
        
        <div class="document-details">
            <h3>üìã Document Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Document ID:</strong> <%= documentId %></p>
            <p><strong>Document Type:</strong> <%= documentType %></p>
            <p><strong>File Name:</strong> <%= fileName %></p>
            <p><strong>Company:</strong> <%= companyName %></p>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= status.toUpperCase() %></p>
        </div>
        
        <% if (status === 'verified' && verifiedBy && verifiedAt) { %>
        <div class="verification-info">
            <h3>‚úÖ Verification Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Verified By:</strong> <%= verifiedBy %></p>
            <p><strong>Verified At:</strong> <%= new Date(verifiedAt).toLocaleString() %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>üéâ Congratulations!</h3>
            <p>Your document has been successfully verified. This means:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your document meets all our requirements</li>
                <li>Your account verification level has been updated</li>
                <li>You can now access additional platform features</li>
                <li>Your company profile shows verified status</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <% } else if (status === 'rejected') { %>
        <div class="rejection-reason">
            <h3>‚ùå Rejection Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reason || 'Document does not meet our verification requirements' %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>üîÑ What You Can Do Next</h3>
            <p>Don't worry! You can resubmit your document with the following improvements:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Ensure the document is clear and legible</li>
                <li>Make sure all required information is visible</li>
                <li>Check that the document is not expired</li>
                <li>Verify that the document type matches what was requested</li>
                <li>Upload in a supported format (PDF, JPG, PNG)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <center>
            <a href="https://iptruck.com/documents/<%= documentId %>" class="button">View Document</a>
        </center>
        
        <% if (status === 'verified') { %>
        <p><strong>Benefits of Verification:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>üîí Enhanced trust and credibility</li>
            <li>üìà Better visibility in search results</li>
            <li>üí∞ Access to premium bookings</li>
            <li>‚≠ê Improved customer confidence</li>
            <li>üöÄ Faster transaction processing</li>
        </ul>
        <% } %>
        
        <p><strong>Need Help?</strong></p>
        <p>If you have questions about the verification process or need assistance with document submission, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a></p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing IpTruck and for maintaining high standards of documentation.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The IpTruck Verification Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You received this email because you submitted a document for verification.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
